==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Windmill
<hw>Wind"mill`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A mill operated by
the power of the wind, usually by the action of the wind upon oblique
vanes or sails which radiate from a horizontal shaft.</def>
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Windore</ent>⟦br⟧
